Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,（失蹤人口 神戶鹽）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我究竟瞭解砂糖有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妳認得這女孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也許松坂小姐綁架這女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打攪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！
